ActPhysical Activity and Sport Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Honourable Jane Philpott as the Minister for the purposes of the Act in respect of physical activity and Designating the Honourable Carla Qualtrough as the Minister for the purposes of the Act in respect of sport
PrecisOrder (1) repealing the P.C. 2003-942 of June 12, 2003; (2) designating the Honourable Jane Philpott, a member of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the Physical Activity and Sport Act in respect of physical activity; and (3) designating the Honourable Carla Qualtrough, a member of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the Physical Activity and Sport Act in respect of sport.
